title: Milkcrate Cafe
text: “Serving Two Great Philadelphia Locations!” Fishtown400 E. Girard ave.phila, pa WEST PHILLY4435 Baltimore ave.phila, pa Our HoursMonday–Sunday:8am–3pm “The Finer Vinyl Diner”Milkcrate Cafe is a vinyl record boutique and cafe with locations in the heart of Fishtown and West Philadelphia. We offer thousands of hand-picked new and rare vintage rock, soul and jazz vinyl records, along with new and used turntables, speakers and receivers.Milkcrate Cafe exclusively brews and sells blends by Caffè Umbria. Our menu features a variety of fast, simple and creative breakfast, brunch and lunch items that has been locally and nationally recognized.
